; Test C directive (price_conversion_directive)
; Exercise the C line for price conversion

C 1.00 EUR = $1.10

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    10.00 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food             10.00 EUR    10.00 EUR
                                Assets:Cash              -10.00 EUR            0
end test
